oji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:04:46.000Z","msg":"中學唔洗死讀爛讀就夠分入教育系<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一出黎就有31k 年年跳point<br />\n好彩既撞正退休升埋主任70k起跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一返工已經可以分期買車<br />\n做幾年野已經夠買樓<br />\n識朋友30歲已經買左3層樓，問我上車點解咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時經過學校見到停車場泊滿晒靚車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5點收工時一架一架排隊不停沖閘走人<br />\n<br />\n呢年WFH淨係zoom半日，仲可以一路上堂一路睇av 同炒股，有老師仲要上埋新聞<br />\n<br />\n然後德育堂教人財富管理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生心理/學業/朋輩/屋企有事根本唔會主動處理，成班淨係識不停卸膊同扮睇唔到，甚至有D笑埋你一份<br />\n<br />\n大多數學生都會忍住啖氣就算，唔好彩既好似今次新聞咁，最後班教畜味又係沙下冧當無件事，繼續年年跳point<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5780648c9cce5425b9ee8eec1d75651f9a0da31f","tid":2488642,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:05:48.000Z","msg":"教畜死全家"},{"pid":"65b29c46b42422b5bd55e74c0d1fd0b43a67f723","tid":2488642,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:07:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9116c66cbf4e776befb3924529f64f0dc4591ca","tid":2488642,"uid":146668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:18:27.000Z","msg":"正仆街"},{"pid":"1dc54a3412c59884b1d61ebcc18970a7b0cc28a5","tid":2488642,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:19:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28c46fa629e69221b3623fa7a3cc92bfe44946d","tid":2488642,"uid":273363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:20:49.000Z"